en.name: Accuracy International AT-XC 7.62x51mm Sniper Rifle
en.description: Introducing the Accuracy International AT-XC rifle. After continuous research and development and exhaustive testing, Accuracy International has created a new generation of a short action rifles with enhanced features. The AT-XC answers the call for modern action with durability, safety, ease of use, and an increased feature set for the competitive shooter. The AT-Xc builds on AI's legacy of engineering and innovation that has made it a world leader in bolt action rifle technology. The AT-XC is a multi-caliber bolt action rifle with quick change barrel capability, two stage competition trigger with adjustable shoe. A cut rifled, high precision, barrel is available in 6mm Creedmoor and 6.5 Creedmoor. The 7075 t6 allow chassis treatment is Mil Std Hardcoat Anodize with a Cerakote finish.

en.name: AC-TX 7.62x51 22 inch stainless steel threaded barrel
en.description: A 20 inch (508mm) stainless steel threaded barrel for the Remington Model 700 sniper rifle chambered in 7.62x51 NATO ammo.
